          Extension for Simple Challenge/Response", RFC 2195, MCI,
          September 1997.

[RFC2245] Newman, C., "Anonymous SASL Mechanism", RFC 2245, Innosoft,
          November 1997. 

[RFC2444] Newman, C., "The One-Time-Password SASL Mechanism", RFC
