[RFC2595] Newman, C., "Using TLS with IMAP, POP3 and ACAP", RFC 2595,
          Innosoft, June 1999.

[RFC2808] Nystrom, M., "The SecurID(r) SASL Mechanism", RFC 2808,
          April 2000.

